name: Cosy Knit Wrap
description:
PRODUCT DETAILS
THE COSY KNIT WRAP – VERSATILE HEAVY-WEIGHT SOFT DRAPE SHAWL.
Wrap up in luxury with the cosy Knit Wrap. Crafted from pure viscose derived from bamboo, this knitted shawl comes in a premium, heavyweight true knit. With its two-tone effect and soft drape, this knitted wrap is ideal for snuggling on the couch or when stepping out on a cold winter morning. Complete with an easy-remove care label, this luxuriously-soft shawl is approximately 70 in x 32 in, making it the perfect piece to wrap up in when lounging around at home or on the move.
Available in both Storm and Dove, the cosy Knit Wrap features a two-tone effect with a contrast natural white knit. We're pleased to say that the cosy Knit Wrap is made from 100% bamboo viscose. Not only does this mean you're wrapping up in a breathable, durable piece of knitwear that's great for your skin, but it's great for the planet too. Fast growing and regenerating, some species of bamboo shoot up as much as 3 feet a day! New stems are able to be harvested again and again. Try to wrap your mind around that as you wrap up in this gorgeous wrap.
FEATURES & FIT

Heavyweight 12-gauge true knit
Soft drape
Two-tone effect
Dimensions:  70" x 31"

 
Why Bamboo?
Why Bamboo Sleep Wrap?
Boody creates affordable luxury by building everyday essentials and underwear from viscose derived from bamboo. The result is a silky smooth base layer that keeps you cool and comfortable with seam-free stretch. Our bamboo fabric maintains it’s shape and is great for sensitive skin. Bamboo fibers are naturally smooth and round with no sharp spurs to irritate skin. Try the cooling comfort of the Boody Sleep Wrap for yourself. This versatile shawl will quickly become your go-to lounge staple.
FABRIC & CARE



Care: Machine wash and dry according to instructions on the care label using a mild, eco-friendly laundry detergent.


Content: 100% viscose made from organically-grown bamboo
Harvested in FSC-certified fields in the Sichuan Province of China, our organically grown bamboo is used to create our signature soft and durable fabric. Boody is naturally breathable, antibacterial, thermo-regulating and hypoallergenic for pure comfort all day long.

details:
Love your smile and the planet with our activated charcoal toothpaste. With bold flavours that pack a punch, giving you a seriously strong smile that's a little bit brighter.

Each carefully sourced ingredient has its own health benefit. With Coconut, Calendula and a unique blend of oils to freshen breath and provide anti-bacterial and anti-inflammatory properties. Activated Charcoal removes plaque whilst naturally whitens teeth, and xylitol to help protect against decay and maintain a healthy pH balance

A perfect addition to your plastic free bathroom for a mouth feeling as fresh as if you had just come from the dentist. Clean teeth, clean ingredients and a clean conscience.

100% Natural, Vegan & Zero Waste.

Free from Fluoride, SLS, Triclosan, Glycerine & Palm Oil.

A pack of three or five bamboo nail polish wipes. Can be used with your normal natural nail polish remover.

What they are made from?

Bamboo, Rayon, Felt. Approx 3" (7.5cm) squares

Why are they fabulous?

Reusable, plastic free and biodegradable.

How to care for them...

Rinse whilst still wet (super important), and leave to dry to reuse. Some staining may stay on cloth from polish - this is normal but will not affect use.

Make sure not to leave the used pads on delicate surfaces and please do not flush these!

Delivery Information

Standard Shipping - £3.95

International Shipping -£6.95

Returns Information

Our policy is valid for a period of 14 calendar days from the date of the purchase. We do not offer refunds however you can return the product for an exchange. If the period of 14 days has elapsed since the purchase, we can’t, unfortunately, offer you an exchange.

name: X Factor Stain Remover Spray 700ml
description:
Our Xfactor Stain Remover spray is a powerful spot cleaner and stain remover, it really does have the ‘Xfactor’ when it comes to removing stains. Its super potent penetrating foam action removes the toughest of stains and sticky marks throughout your home. 
As a plant based, vegan friendly, natural stain remover spray it is easy to use and a handy cupboard must have for those sticky spillages, scuff marks, permanent marker and pen accidents that just happen!  

Free from Solvents, VOC’s, EDTA, NTA, fragrance and dye, APEs.
Fast acting stain cleaner 
Penetrating foaming action
Reduced use of hazardous substances 
Phosphate and phosphonate free

Areas of Use

Suitable for use on hard surfaces
Removes sticky spillages and residue
Removes Scuff Marks, Permanent Marker Biro

Instructions for Use 
Apply a small amount of XFactor Stain Remover cleaner to a damp cloth and wipe clean. For heavy cleaning, spray directly on to the surface, leave for a few seconds and wipe clean with a damp cloth. Always patch test on an inconspicuous area first.  
This product is not suitable for use on porous surfaces and should not be used as a Multi-Purpose Cleaner across widespread areas. 





Loved by Professionals, Approved by the Planet
100% Made in Britain
Vegan Friendly, Natural Plant Based Cleaning Product
Ethical & Eco Friendly Sustainable Cleaning 
Highly Biodegradable Ingredients
B Corp Certified
Never Tested on Animals
Pet Safe
100% Recycled & Recyclable Plastic Bottle Packaging
